      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Fixer-Upper \u2014 A Project Car with Potential! This car is priced to reflect its current condition honestly \u2014 it's showing significant wear both inside and out, and will need some meaningful attention to get it back to its best. The exterior has noticeable dents, scratches, and rust, and the interior shows heavy use. Mechanically, it runs but has known issues that will need addressing. If you're a hands-on buyer, a DIY mechanic, or just need basic transportation on a tight budget, this could be your opportunity! What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just honest value. \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f",
