    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Honest Price, Honest Car \u2014 Budget Wheels That Get the Job Done!** We believe in straight talk here \u2014 this vehicle is showing significant wear and has mechanical issues that will need attention. It's not a showroom star, but for a buyer who's handy, looking for a parts car, or just needs the most basic transportation on a tight budget, this could be your opportunity. Priced accordingly so you know exactly what you're getting into \u2014 no surprises, just an honest deal. Come take a look and decide for yourself!",
      "price": 3000.0,
